Are there tax penalties for moving my existing retirement account into Gold?
No. The process you are referring to is usually called a "rollover" or "transfer". With this process, you will not incur any tax penalties.


What are the benefits of a self-directed IRA?
First, this is a great step in protecting your future! Secondly, depending on the type of IRA, there could be tax advantages (eg. tax-deferred or tax-free growth). We would recommend 
						AMERICAN BULLION for this. 
					     You can also contact them from the USA by calling (888) 779-9890 toll-free.


